    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "yeah exactly. that's it. there's no \"way out\" because there's nothing left to find. it's just... exhausting to keep pretending to be a person when the actual person is long gone. it feels like i'm carrying around a corpse. why does it even matter if this shell keeps going or not?",
